%@CR:MSE10010@%%@4@%%@AB@%A Note about Operating-System Terms%@AE@%%@EH@%%@NL@%
%@NL@%
%@CR:MSE10011@%%@4@%Microsoft documentation uses the term "OS/2" to refer to the OS/2%@EH@%
systemsÄÄMicrosoft Operating System/2 (MS(R) OS/2) and IBM(R) OS/2.
Similarly, the term "DOS" refers to both the MS-DOS(R) and IBM Personal
Computer DOS operating systems. The name of a specific operating system is
used when it is necessary to note features unique to that system.%@NL@%
%@NL@%
