%@NL@%
%@CR:MSE9R253@%%@4@%The return value is a structure of type %@AB@%cmdDesc%@AE@%. The structure describes the%@EH@%
command corresponding to the keystroke pressed.%@NL@%
%@NL@%
%@4@%%@AB@%ş  See also%@AE@%%@EH@%%@NL@%
